    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋王之路 是唯一的国际象棋职业模拟器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创建你的角色并攀登职业阶梯</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/13be4e6967db996b025c925cd60f3ea9.poster.avif?t=1771392133\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/13be4e6967db996b025c925cd60f3ea9.webm?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/13be4e6967db996b025c925cd60f3ea9.mp4?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演国际象棋选手的一生，从一个有前途的年轻天才到一位经验丰富的高手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个有前途的年轻天才开始，成为世界级的国际象棋大师。争取棋坛不朽！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提高你的国际象棋水平</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/c945775fc2b7b6e37a386c06eef03d63.poster.avif?t=1771392133\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/c945775fc2b7b6e37a386c06eef03d63.webm?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/c945775fc2b7b6e37a386c06eef03d63.mp4?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过一个始终陪伴你职业生涯的教练，挑战AI对手，解决难题以及不断发展的开局库，提升你的真实国际象棋技能……但要小心失误！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>智能AI系统提升你的棋艺</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在AI系统的帮助下实现你的梦想职业，它将指导你选择最佳走法，挑选正确的开局，超越并智胜最强的对手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/2738953c815eda65b4c8d9feffd612b8.poster.avif?t=1771392133\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/2738953c815eda65b4c8d9feffd612b8.webm?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248900/extras/2738953c815eda65b4c8d9feffd612b8.mp4?t=1771392133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >截止日期、紧张的预算、比赛费用、紧张的比赛……职业国际象棋选手的生活并不容易，但你拥有轻松管理每一个方面的所有工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>成为国际象棋大师</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能登顶吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你准备好留下你的印记并成为传奇了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋盘在等待。 <strong>今天就开始在 棋王之路 中的终身旅程吧！</strong></p>",
